T1  - Financial Markets and Incomplete Information: Frontiers of Modern Financial Theory, Volume 2, Sudipto Bhattacharya and George M. Constantinides, eds. Totowa, N.J.: Rowman and Littlefield, 1989. 361 pp., ISBN 0-8476-7597-1
PY  - 1990
